{"tid":923391,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拿華斯：3奪歐聯都無得踢","createTime":"2018-12-01T08:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T10:56:24.000Z","uid":32938,"like":96,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"513389fd8e6652f58890adb9d87891ebeb871df2","tid":923391,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:06:29.000Z","msg":"雖然皇馬改由蘇拿利執教後表現已有起色，但在去仗西甲以0：3負於伊巴腳下明顯反映球隊仍不在最佳狀態。此外，皇馬目前有部份球員不滿上陣時間的安排，像近年的正選門將拿華斯則對傳媒炮轟會方以高圖爾斯取代他的做法，他不忿道：「我由助球隊3奪歐聯冠軍，到現在完全沒有機會上陣。」<br />\n<br />\n拿華斯以外，艾斯高亦對球隊主帥頗為不滿，有指因他與蘇拿利鬧不和而無緣上陣近日賽事，而更因而考慮離隊。"},{"pid":"8231f3d24c21d9b1901a894a0cff58573fcf4eed","tid":923391,"uid":34293,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"搵黑氣石受靶唔洗你上場執波啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513c796193cfd2c7bde0a1e44ae12e23e20cce57","tid":923391,"uid":15830,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:15:02.000Z","msg":"矮是原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e530fdf30f1c2d01f0f3a9ebf51de7fa6dec27bf","tid":923391,"uid":60506,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:17:02.000Z","msg":"拿華斯去祖喇"},{"pid":"667b76992757f9513bd80c83f3fea00252d4a37c","tid":923391,"uid":43785,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:18:39.000Z","msg":"拿華斯會差過高圖爾斯？<br />\n人地為左下年世三加入炸"},{"pid":"727c691c42c415b4cf5ea8a2c04dfbeec60e36b2","tid":923391,"uid":6577,"like":65,"dislike":9,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:19:24.000Z","msg":"真係好慘 其實佢去5大聯賽任何1隊都可以打必然正選"},{"pid":"4b956437ac8cec3be24309e1ecb578bd5382a9a1","tid":923391,"uid":23833,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:42:21.000Z","msg":"走啦拿華斯<br />\n好似c朗咁"},{"pid":"bffd5af9a838a992decec0e1bbc99653d8a69cd8","tid":923391,"uid":8612,"like":3,"dislike":29,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018